{"tid":1725841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停止分化，一致對外","createTime":"2019-11-16T01:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:25:13.000Z","uid":36058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b9810659da77cf8e91357af6ee1b61fb4f09b7","tid":1725841,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"請唔好再推分化po，MK、勇武、學者、學生、和理非，大家mentality 唔同，所以造就不同人生，中共港共一意孤行，極權高壓，導致大家殊途同歸，就係香港滅族，但係亦係正正大家mentality 唔同，先至導致運動空前成功，因為每個人都可以按照自己能力性格發揮所長貢獻運動，但水能載舟亦能覆舟，正正係因為大家唔同，所以被敵人利用作為分化切入點。請停止分化，和而不同，一致抗敵。"},{"pid":"9c8ec74af049d68aab4ee849da0503578f314d22","tid":1725841,"uid":338743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be21e095998ed2fdec5a1136181fd5d9d82887b8","tid":1725841,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f7734c594445b494c195510ae2921c9cf67fea","tid":1725841,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"覺得香港已經被中共分化了"},{"pid":"a56c5f481b23c3d2844a81e8297a3473283aadce","tid":1725841,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:58:53.000Z","msg":"重新團結，重整旗鼓。<br />\n<br />\n大原則：不受傷，不被捕"},{"pid":"d134f3e3a8aa4eab0607731e9356a6a0e19d4781","tid":1725841,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"Super REUNION"},{"pid":"8db680dfa4f5c1fd493cebda7365931cc1e31655","tid":1725841,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:25:13.000Z","msg":"記住終極大佬係港共"}]}